          "params": [],
          "returnType": null,
          "description": "Carrier oscillator frequency in Hz. Range 0..20000, default 440. Lower frequencies (1–60 Hz) produce tremolo-like pulsing; mid-range values (100–1000 Hz) give the characteristic robotic ring-mod sound; high values shift sidebands above the audible fundamental."
        },
        {
          "name": "waveform",
